#~ msgstr "„%s“: %d"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "**Liked Songs: duplicate detection**\n"
#~ "- Before adding a track to `likedSongs.txt`, the file is now read and "
#~ "checked for an existing entry with the same text. If the track is already "
#~ "present, it is not written again and NVDA announces \"Already in liked "
#~ "songs: [track]\" instead. This prevents the list from accumulating "
#~ "repeated entries when the same track is recognised or copied multiple "
#~ "times during a session.\n"
#~ "**F2 in station browser: 4-press behaviour now mirrors Ctrl+Win+I**\n"
#~ "- The in-dialog F2 handler (`_whats_playing_from_dialog`) has been "
#~ "rewritten to match `script_whatsPlaying` press-for-press:\n"
#~ "- **1×** — announce the currently playing station and track\n"
#~ "- **2×** — open the station details dialog (delayed 350 ms so a 3rd press "
#~ "can cancel it)\n"
#~ "- **3×** — copy ICY track title to clipboard; fall back to Shazam if no "
#~ "metadata is available\n"
#~ "- **4×** — force Shazam music recognition regardless of ICY metadata, "
#~ "then reset the counter\n"
#~ "- Previously the handler merged the 3rd and all subsequent presses into a "
#~ "single `elif count >= 2` branch, so the 4th press was never reached. A "
#~ "cancellation token is now also passed into the 3rd-press background "
#~ "thread so that a 4th press arriving while the thread is still running "
#~ "correctly aborts the clipboard/Shazam action before the forced-"
#~ "recognition path takes over.\n"
#~ "**Music Recognizer: improved recognition of non-mainstream tracks**\n"
#~ "- Previously, the signature generator stopped processing audio after ~3.1 "
#~ "seconds or 255 peaks, whichever came first. The full 12-second audio "
#~ "sample is now used to build the fingerprint, sending significantly richer "
#~ "data to Shazam. This hopefully improves recognition accuracy for folk, "
#~ "regional, and other non-mainstream music.\n"
#~ "**All Stations tab: Sort combo box**\n"
#~ "- Added a *Sort* combo box to the All Stations tab, placed before the "
#~ "Country filter. Options are **Alphabetical** (default) and **By Rating** "
#~ "(sorted by vote count, highest first). Changing the sort order instantly "
#~ "re-sorts the current station list without triggering a new network "
#~ "request.\n"
#~ "**Settings: SAPI5 voice selector for track change announcements**\n"
#~ "- Added a *SAPI5 voice* dropdown to the settings panel, appearing below "
#~ "the existing *Track change voice* option. - When SAPI5 is selected as the "
#~ "announcement voice, users can now choose which installed SAPI5 voice to "
#~ "use. The list is populated automatically from the system's available "
#~ "voices. Selecting *Default (system)* uses whatever voice Windows has set "
#~ "as the default. The dropdown is disabled when NVDA is selected as the "
#~ "announcement voice, or when auto-announce is turned off.\n"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "**Oblíbené skladby: detekce duplicit**\n"
#~ "- Před přidáním skladby do souboru `likedSongs.txt` se nyní soubor načte "
#~ "a zkontroluje, zda již neobsahuje záznam se stejným textem. Pokud je "
#~ "skladba již v seznamu, nezapíše se znovu a NVDA místo toho oznámí: „Již v "
#~ "oblíbených skladbách: [název skladby]“. Tím se zabrání hromadění "
#~ "duplicitních záznamů v seznamu, když je stejná skladba během relace "
#~ "rozpoznána nebo zkopírována vícekrát.\n"
#~ "**F2 v prohlížeči stanic: chování při 4 stisknutích nyní odpovídá "
#~ "kombinaci kláves Ctrl+Win+I**\n"
#~ "- Obslužná rutina klávesy F2 v dialogovém okně "
#~ "(`_whats_playing_from_dialog`) byla přepracována tak, aby se shodovala s "
#~ "funkcí `script_whatsPlaying` při každém stisknutí:\n"
#~ "- **1×** — oznámí aktuálně přehrávanou stanici a skladbu\n"
#~ "- **2×** — otevře dialog s podrobnostmi o stanici (se zpožděním 350 ms, "
#~ "aby jej bylo možné zrušit třetím stisknutím)\n"
#~ "- **3×** — zkopíruje název skladby z ICY do schránky; pokud nejsou k "
#~ "dispozici metadata, použije Shazam\n"
#~ "- **4×** — vynutí rozpoznání hudby pomocí Shazamu bez ohledu na metadata "
#~ "ICY a poté vynuluje počítadlo\n"
#~ "- Dříve handler sloučil třetí a všechna následující stisknutí do jediné "
#~ "větve `elif count >= 2`, takže ke čtvrtému stisknutí nikdy nedošlo. Nyní "
#~ "se do pozadí vlákna třetího stisknutí předává také token zrušení, takže "
#~ "pokud dojde ke čtvrtému stisknutí, zatímco vlákno stále běží, správně se "
#~ "přeruší akce schránky/Shazamu, než převezme kontrolu cesta vynuceného "
#~ "rozpoznávání.\n"
#~ "**Rozpoznávač hudby: vylepšené rozpoznávání nemainstreamových skladeb**\n"
#~ "- Dříve generátor signatury zastavil zpracování zvuku po ~3,1 sekundách "
#~ "nebo 255 vrcholech, podle toho, co nastalo dříve. K vytvoření otisku se "
#~ "nyní používá celý 12sekundový zvukový vzorek, což posílá do Shazamu "
#~ "výrazně bohatší data. To snad zlepší přesnost rozpoznávání u folkové, "
#~ "regionální a jiné nemainstreamové hudby.\n"
#~ "**Karta Všechny stanice: Rozbalovací seznam Seřadit**\n"
#~ "- Na kartu Všechny stanice bylo přidáno rozbalovací menu *Seřadit*, "
#~ "umístěné před filtrem Země. Možnosti jsou **Abecedně** (výchozí) a "
#~ "**Podle hodnocení** (seřazeno podle počtu hlasů, nejvyšší jako první). "
#~ "Změna pořadí okamžitě přeseřadí aktuální seznam stanic, aniž by došlo k "
#~ "novému síťovému požadavku.\n"
#~ "**Nastavení: Výběr hlasu SAPI5 pro hlášení změny skladby**\n"
#~ "- Do panelu nastavení bylo přidáno rozevírací menu *Hlas SAPI5*, které se "
#~ "zobrazuje pod stávající možností *Hlas pro změnu skladby*. - Pokud je "
#~ "jako hlas pro hlášení vybrán SAPI5, mohou uživatelé nyní zvolit, který z "
#~ "nainstalovaných hlasů SAPI5 se má použít. Seznam se automaticky vyplní z "
#~ "hlasů dostupných v systému. Výběrem možnosti *Výchozí (systém)* se "
#~ "použije hlas, který má Windows nastaven jako výchozí. Rozbalovací nabídka "
#~ "je deaktivována, pokud je jako hlas pro hlášení vybrán NVDA nebo pokud je "
#~ "automatické hlášení vypnuto.\n"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "- Change reorder favorite key to comma because * doesn't work for many "
#~ "keyboard layout.\n"
#~ "**Fixed**\n"
#~ "- `ctrl+win+r` and other hotkeys silently failing to reopen the station "
#~ "browser dialog after it had been hidden at least once.\n"
#~ "\n"
#~ "**Root cause:** NVDA maintains an internal popup counter that is "
#~ "incremented by `prePopup()` and decremented by `postPopup()`. "
#~ "`prePopup()` was called once when the dialog was first created, but none "
#~ "of the code paths that hide the dialog (`_on_close_btn`, "
#~ "`_on_window_close`, ESC key, Enter on Close button, Alt+K, "
#~ "`_force_destroy`) ever called `postPopup()`. The counter therefore grew "
#~ "by one on every open/hide cycle and never decreased. After enough cycles "
#~ "NVDA interpreted the accumulated count as \"another popup is already "
#~ "open\" and silently blocked subsequent `Show()` calls, causing the dialog "
#~ "to appear completely unresponsive to all hotkeys with no error logged.\n"
#~ "\n"
#~ "**Fix:** Added `gui.mainFrame.postPopup()` after every `self.Hide()` and "
#~ "`self.Destroy()` call in `radioDialog.py`. Added a matching "
#~ "`gui.mainFrame.prePopup()` in `_open_dialog()` (`__init__.py`) for the re-"
#~ "show path, so each `prePopup` is correctly paired with a `postPopup` for "
#~ "the full lifetime of the dialog.\n"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "- A tecla de atalho para reordenar favoritos foi alterada para vírgula "
#~ "(`,`), pois o `*` não funciona em muitos layouts de teclado.\n"
#~ "**Corrigido**\n"
#~ "- `ctrl+win+r` e outros atalhos falhando silenciosamente ao tentar "
#~ "reabrir o diálogo do navegador de estações após ele ter sido ocultado "
#~ "pelo menos uma vez.\n"
#~ "**Causa raiz:** O NVDA mantém um contador interno de popups que é "
#~ "incrementado por `prePopup()` e decrementado por `postPopup()`. O "
#~ "`prePopup()` era chamado uma vez quando o diálogo era criado pela "
#~ "primeira vez, mas nenhum dos caminhos de código que ocultam o diálogo "
#~ "(`_on_close_btn`, `_on_window_close`, tecla ESC, Enter no botão Fechar, "
#~ "Alt+K, `_force_destroy`) jamais chamava `postPopup()`. O contador, "
#~ "portanto, aumentava em um a cada ciclo de abertura/ocultação e nunca "
#~ "diminuía. Após ciclos suficientes, o NVDA interpretava a contagem "
#~ "acumulada como \"outro popup já está aberto\" e bloqueava silenciosamente "
#~ "as chamadas subsequentes de `Show()`, fazendo com que o diálogo parecesse "
#~ "completamente sem resposta a todos os atalhos, sem nenhum erro "
#~ "registrado.\n"
#~ "**Correção:** Adicionado `gui.mainFrame.postPopup()` após cada chamada de "
#~ "`self.Hide()` e `self.Destroy()` em `radioDialog.py`. Adicionado um "
#~ "`gui.mainFrame.prePopup()` correspondente em `_open_dialog()` "
#~ "(`__init__.py`) para o caminho de reexibição, de modo que cada `prePopup` "
#~ "seja corretamente emparelhado com um `postPopup` durante todo o ciclo de "
#~ "vida do diálogo.\n"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "**Focus management after item removal**\n"
#~ "- Favorites list: after deleting a station, focus and selection "
#~ "automatically move to the next item in the list. If the deleted station "
#~ "was the last one, focus moves to the previous item. If the list becomes "
#~ "empty, focus moves to the Play button.\n"
#~ "- Liked Songs list: same behaviour — after removing a song, focus stays "
#~ "on the next item, or moves to the Refresh button if the list is empty.\n"
#~ "**Delete key shortcut**\n"
#~ "- Pressing `Delete` while a station is selected in the Favorites list now "
#~ "triggers the Delete Station button (equivalent to clicking it), provided "
#~ "the button is enabled.\n"
#~ "- Pressing `Delete` while a song is selected in the Liked Songs list now "
#~ "triggers the Remove button, provided the button is enabled.\n"
#~ "- In both cases the key has no effect when no valid item is selected or "
#~ "the corresponding button is disabled.\n"
#~ "- Added a new \"Mute notifications\" checkbox to FreeRadio settings "
#~ "(unchecked by default).\n"
#~ "- When enabled, NVDA no longer announces station changes, playback state "
#~ "changes (play, pause, stop), or recording events (started, stopped, "
#~ "finished).\n"
#~ "- Error messages, favourites feedback, music recognition results, and "
#~ "update notifications are intentionally unaffected.\n"
#~ "- Added an unassigned script_toggleMuteNotifications input gesture that "
#~ "toggles the setting on the fly. Assign a key combination via NVDA's Input "
#~ "Gestures dialog under the FreeRadio category.\n"
#~ "- Two module-level helpers (_notify, _notify_on_demand) centralise the "
#~ "mute check, keeping call sites clean.\n"
#~ "**Changed: Search now filters by selected country automatically**\n"
#~ "- Search queries are now scoped to the selected country. When a country "
#~ "is chosen in the combo box, results are fetched from the API already "
#~ "filtered by that country rather than searching globally and filtering "
#~ "locally afterward.\n"
#~ "- The Search button has been removed. Results update automatically as you "
#~ "type (debounced, 500 ms delay), so a manual trigger is no longer needed.\n"
#~ "- Removed the Enter key and Alt+A shortcuts that previously triggered a "
#~ "manual search.\n"
#~ "- The search status message has been shortened. It now reads `\"query\": "
#~ "N in Country` instead of the previous `Search \"query\": N results (N in "
#~ "Country)`.\n"
#~ "- The key used for reordering favorites was changed from X to * (star).\n"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "**Gestão do foco após remoção de itens**\n"
